items.title: Vintage 1970s Leather Biker Jacket
items.description: Genuine heavy-grain leather with authentic patina. All zippers work perfectly. Fits like a men's medium. Some minor scuffing on the elbows adds to the character.

items.title: Handmade Walnut Coffee Table
items.description: Custom built solid walnut table with steel hairpin legs. Finished with natural tung oil. Dimensions: 48"L x 24"W x 18"H. Beautiful wood grain patterns.

items.title: Mechanical Keyboard - Keychron Q1 Custom
items.description: Fully assembled with Gateron Oil King switches and PBT keycaps. Aluminum body feels very premium and heavy. Hot-swappable PCB.

items.title: Outdoor Camping Tent - 4 Person Capacity
items.description: Used for three seasons. No tears or leaks, but some slight mud staining on the rainfly. All poles and stakes are included. Easy 10-minute setup.

items.title: Noise Canceling Headphones
items.description: Brand new, never opened. Received as a gift but I already own a pair. Industry-leading noise cancellation and 30-hour battery life.

items.title: Classic Office Chair - Size B
items.description: A classic office chair. Features lumbar support and adjustable armrests. Mesh is in perfect condition with no sagging. Slight scratches on the base from normal use.

items.title: Vacuum Cleaner
items.description: Works great, just upgraded to the V15. Attachments included.

items.title: PS5 Digital Edition
